flowchart TB
    L1["Layer 1: Authentication\nWho is this person?\nAuth.js session or API token"]
    L2["Layer 2: Identity & Role\nPlatform role: HR-000 to HR-500\nBusiness model roles: product-scoped"]
    L3["Layer 3: Capability Resolution\n32 capabilities mapped to roles\ncan(user, capability) -> boolean"]
    L4["Layer 4: Agent Grant Intersection\nTool-to-grant mapping\nEffective = user capabilities AND agent grants"]
    L5["Layer 5: Execution Mode\nImmediate: execute now\nProposal: human approval required"]

    L1 -->|narrows| L2
    L2 -->|narrows| L3
    L3 -->|narrows| L4
    L4 -->|narrows| L5

    L5 -->|immediate| EXEC["Tool Executes\nResult recorded"]
    L5 -->|proposal| APPROVE["Human Approves\nor Rejects"]
    APPROVE -->|approved| EXEC
    APPROVE -->|rejected| LOG["Rejection\nLogged"]

    style L1 fill:#0d47a1,color:#fff
    style L2 fill:#1565c0,color:#fff
    style L3 fill:#1976d2,color:#fff
    style L4 fill:#1e88e5,color:#fff
    style L5 fill:#2196f3,color:#fff
    style EXEC fill:#2e7d32,color:#fff
    style APPROVE fill:#f57f17,color:#fff
    style LOG fill:#c62828,color:#fff
